# textdomain: vl_cavesounds
Turn cave sounds for yourself or another player on or off.=Vklopi ali izklopi jamske zvoke zase ali za druge.

You need the debug privilege in order to turn cave sounds on or off for somebody else!=Za vklop ali izklop jamskih zvokov za nekoga drugega potrebujete privilegij za razhroščevanje!

Could not find player @1!=Igralca @1 ni bilo mogoče najti!
off=izklop
on=vklop
Set cave sounds for @1 to: @2=Nastavi jamske zvoke za @1 na: @2
